Class PropertyConstraint

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--gnu.mapping.Constraint
        |
        +--gnu.mapping.PropertyConstraint
public class PropertyConstraint
extends Constraint

The Constraint for a Binding that may have arbitrary associated properties. The Bindings's value felds points to a Object array, whose even elements contain "keys" where the following odd element contains an associated value. This provides support for the "symbol" data types of Common Lisp and Emacs Lisp.
